## рџ“Ѓ Folder Structure Best Practices

### Use Folders When:

1. **Content naturally groups**:
   ```
   interview/
   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ questions/
   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ fundamentals.md
   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ system-design.md
   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ cloud.md
   ```

2. **You expect expansion**:
   ```
   interview/
   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ scenarios/
   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ README.md
   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ e-commerce.md
   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ social-media.md
   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ video-streaming.md
   ```

3. **You need navigation**:
   ```
   interview/
   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ glossary/
   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ README.md  # Index with links
   в”‚   в”њв”Ђв”Ђ core-concepts.md
   в”‚   в””в”Ђв”Ђ advanced.md
   ```

### Folder Naming

- Use semantic names: `questions/`, `scenarios/`, `glossary/`
- Use hyphens for multi-word: `system-design/`, `cloud-architecture/`
- Use numbers ONLY when sequence matters: `01_fundamentals/`, `02_advanced/`

